{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Immersive Action</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hack terminals while shooting cyber magic bastards while switching guns with the right arm and casting spells with the left one.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103640/extras/2024.12.27_Immersive_Actions.gif?t=1738347379\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Carousel of Guns</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Try all the armory in one go: shoot, throw, pick another one. Destroy enemies with various guns from not-so-boring pistols to void cannons (what the hell is that?!).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103640/extras/2024.12.27_Shooting.gif?t=1738347379\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Arsenal of Cool Spells</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Attacking, protective and supportive magic for all possible cases. Fireballs, electricity, shields, summoning are just a small part of it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103640/extras/2024.25.12_Spells.gif?t=1738347379\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Put Down Badass Bosses</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Destroy Vile Corporate Wizard, Cyber Dragon and other insane cybermagic baddies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103640/extras/2024.12.25_Shooting.gif?t=1738347379\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Fight Gang Hordes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get rid of hordes of bandits, corporates, robots, mages and other bastards! Don't let their cooperative tactics and numbers outplay you.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Humorous Adventure</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Chatty bud stuck in a robot body and cyberwizards mad of money exploiting skeletons will set up a satiric adventure of an old-school cool as heck guy spitting in a face of the world.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Play wireless</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy the game without limits and wires in a standalone mode.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103640/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738347379","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103640/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738347379","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103640/8aef4c38676dabb444a35ac6a112dc2ae78130c6/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738347379","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103640/8aef4c38676dabb444a35ac6a112dc2ae78130c6/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738347379","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Immersive Action</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hack terminals while shooting cyber magic bastards while switching guns with the right arm and casting spells with the left one.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103640/extras/2024.12.27_Immersive_Actions.gif?t=1738347379\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Carousel of Guns</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Try all the armory in one go: shoot, throw, pick another one. Destroy enemies with various guns from not-so-boring pistols to void cannons (what the hell is that?!).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103640/extras/2024.12.27_Shooting.gif?t=1738347379\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Arsenal of Cool Spells</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Attacking, protective and supportive magic for all possible cases. Fireba